//INSTALLING ACTARSIM
After uncompressing the file
1. Create a new directory where the program will be compiled and installed and change to it

$mkdir ../ActarSim-build
$cd ../ActarSim-build

2. Call cmake to create the makefile adapted to your system

$cmake -DGean4_DIR=/pathToGeant4Instalation/lib/Geant<version> /pathToActarSimSource

3. Compile

$make

4. Install

$make install 